[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 7.0,
    "text": "Since today is show and tell day, you can be my subject."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.0,
    "endTime": 9.0,
    "text": "What do I have to do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.0,
    "endTime": 13.0,
    "text": "Just be your dreamy self and let me show you and tell about you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.0,
    "endTime": 14.0,
    "text": "Hey, do I look okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.0,
    "endTime": 19.0,
    "text": "And then my cat coughed up this thing that kind of looks like George Washington."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.0,
    "endTime": 20.0,
    "text": "Ewww!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.0,
    "endTime": 24.0,
    "text": "Next up is little Susie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.0,
    "endTime": 28.0,
    "text": "Ladies and gentlemen, I give you the world's greatest superhero."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.0,
    "endTime": 29.0,
    "text": "Rub-o-man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.0,
    "endTime": 30.0,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 33.0,
    "text": "A real superhero!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.0,
    "endTime": 37.0,
    "text": "Hey, what are all these kids doing here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 37.0,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 41.0,
    "text": "Now look here, kids."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.0,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "I'm not exactly a real superhero."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.0,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "Sure you're not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 50.0,
    "text": "I've got a real thing for big, strong superheroes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.0,
    "endTime": 53.0,
    "text": "Wanna see me comb my hair really fast?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.0,
    "endTime": 53.0,
    "text": "Help!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.0,
    "endTime": 58.0,
    "text": "The bank is being robbed!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "Is anyone here a superhero?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 61.0,
    "text": "Cool!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.0,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "The bank is being robbed!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.0,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "Yeah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.0,
    "endTime": 68.0,
    "text": "Now Rub-o-man can go smash the bad guy with his Rub-o-powers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.0,
    "endTime": 70.0,
    "text": "Oh, you will pay for this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.0,
    "endTime": 76.0,
    "text": "Uh, look folks, you're gonna have to step back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.0,
    "endTime": 78.0,
    "text": "There's a robbery going on in there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.0,
    "endTime": 78.0,
    "text": "Yes, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.0,
    "endTime": 79.0,
    "text": "No problem, officer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.0,
    "endTime": 80.0,
    "text": "Officer, this is Rub-o-man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.0,
    "endTime": 85.0,
    "text": "He's a superhero and he's here to stop the bad guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 85.0,
    "text": "Yeah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.0,
    "endTime": 87.0,
    "text": "Hey, did you hear that, fellas?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.0,
    "endTime": 88.0,
    "text": "There's a superhero here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.0,
    "endTime": 90.0,
    "text": "Hey, let's go get some donuts!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 91.0,
    "text": "Yeah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.0,
    "endTime": 97.0,
    "text": "I just found out who the bad guy is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.0,
    "endTime": 98.0,
    "text": "It's Sweet Cheeks, the candy-powered villain."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.0,
    "endTime": 102.0,
    "text": "I just love a man who stands up to super villains."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 103.0,
    "text": "Stand back, everybody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.0,
    "endTime": 104.0,
    "text": "Rub-o-man is here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.0,
    "endTime": 104.0,
    "text": "Yeah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.0,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "All right, hold it, hold it, you..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "Yeah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 108.0,
    "text": "Wow!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.0,
    "endTime": 121.0,
    "text": "Did you see the way Bravo Man just let Sweet Cheeks think he was getting away?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.0,
    "endTime": 122.0,
    "text": "You know, you can stop now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.0,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "I already got an A on my project."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 127.0,
    "text": "That was very brave."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.0,
    "endTime": 128.0,
    "text": "I'm gonna get you an A-plus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.0,
    "endTime": 137.0,
    "text": "Joy it brings me to rob and steal and to generally do evil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.0,
    "endTime": 138.0,
    "text": "Now, look here, mister."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.0,
    "endTime": 140.0,
    "text": "Don't force me to whip you right here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.0,
    "endTime": 143.0,
    "text": "How about I whip you with my licorice whip?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.0,
    "endTime": 144.0,
    "text": "Oh, good golly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 145.0,
    "text": "Cool!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 147.0,
    "text": "Sweet Cheeks died of Bravo Man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.0,
    "endTime": 155.0,
    "text": "Yeah, but Bravo Man totally escaped."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.0,
    "endTime": 155.0,
    "text": "Yay!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.0,
    "endTime": 169.0,
    "text": "By stealing all the children's candy, I shall have total control over their snack time."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.0,
    "endTime": 175.0,
    "text": "Okay, candy boy, I didn't want it to have to come to this, but..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.0,
    "endTime": 175.0,
    "text": "Oh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.0,
    "endTime": 178.0,
    "text": "Man, it's dark in here, dark in here, dark in here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.0,
    "endTime": 184.0,
    "text": "Hey, Johnny, I have a plan."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.0,
    "endTime": 189.0,
    "text": "I lure Sweet Cheeks over to this hole and you can beat him up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.0,
    "endTime": 190.0,
    "text": "Excuse me, sir."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.0,
    "endTime": 191.0,
    "text": "Aren't you the evil villain Sweet Cheeks?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.0,
    "endTime": 199.0,
    "text": "I'll bet you're terribly frightened of me, aren't you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.0,
    "endTime": 201.0,
    "text": "Yes, sir, I am."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.0,
    "endTime": 207.0,
    "text": "But it would really scare me if you'd just back up a bit towards that manhole."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.0,
    "endTime": 207.0,
    "text": "Very well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.0,
    "endTime": 207.0,
    "text": "Oh, man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.0,
    "endTime": 208.0,
    "text": "Now's my chance."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.0,
    "endTime": 210.0,
    "text": "I can catch Sweet Cheeks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.0,
    "endTime": 210.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.0,
    "endTime": 211.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.0,
    "endTime": 216.0,
    "text": "Oh, man, that does it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.0,
    "endTime": 217.0,
    "text": "This was my favorite shirt."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.0,
    "endTime": 229.0,
    "text": "I gotta go wash up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.0,
    "endTime": 230.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.0,
    "endTime": 240.0,
    "text": "As a token of my extreme hatred for all people in the world, I shall change this child into a large chocolate bunny."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.0,
    "endTime": 241.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.0,
    "endTime": 242.0,
    "text": "With a caramel center?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.0,
    "endTime": 244.0,
    "text": "With an exceptionally large caramel center."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.0,
    "endTime": 245.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.0,
    "endTime": 251.0,
    "text": "This thing ought to wash me up pretty good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.0,
    "endTime": 253.0,
    "text": "Bravo Man, come quick!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.0,
    "endTime": 255.0,
    "text": "Sweet Cheeks got little Susie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.0,
    "endTime": 255.0,
    "text": "What'd you say?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.0,
    "endTime": 257.0,
    "text": "Are you okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.0,
    "endTime": 262.0,
    "text": "I sure am, thanks to Bravo Man."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.0,
    "endTime": 262.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.0,
    "endTime": 269.0,
    "text": "I'm melting!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.0,
    "endTime": 273.0,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.0,
    "endTime": 276.0,
    "text": "Bravo Man saved us!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.0,
    "endTime": 276.0,
    "text": "Yay!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.0,
    "endTime": 276.0,
    "text": "Ah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.0,
    "endTime": 276.0,
    "text": "Wow!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.0,
    "endTime": 281.0,
    "text": "Bravo Man's the greatest!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.0,
